Pulse Pace Stopwatch Web App
This web application is a unique stopwatch tool created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Key Features

Functionality for starting, stopping, and resetting the stopwatch.
Tracks lap times accurately including milliseconds.
Includes an option to share stopwatch results on social media platforms.
Offers keyboard shortcuts for easy control: 'Space' for Start/Stop, 'r' for Reset, 'l' for Lap.
User-friendly design with a responsive layout for different devices.
How to Use
To utilize this stopwatch web app, simply open the PulsePace.html file in your web browser.

Contributions
We welcome contributions! If you have any suggestions for enhancements or new features, please feel free to raise an issue or submit a pull request. We appreciate your input and efforts to improve this project.
